  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2022-04-26",
    "date": "2023-08-23T16:23:51Z",
    "text": "Healthy Drinking Water Affordability Act or the Healthy H2O Act\n\nThis bill directs the Department of Agriculture to establish a clean drinking water program to provide grants for water quality testing and for the purchase, installation, and maintenance of point-of use and point-of-entry water filtration systems that remove or significantly reduce contaminants in drinking water. Grants may be given to end users (such as homeowners), nonprofit organizations, and government entities."
